@chrismattmann there is an issue in testing this over in DRAT.
OODT 1.2.2 modules use Tika 1.10 and 1.7 dependencies... hence DRAT distribution packages a deployment which inherits the older Tika dependencies transitively. 
We need to upgrade Tika in OODT, as per this PR, test and push a release before we can move forward elsewhere.
